{"word":"σάγμα","slug":"σάγμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σάγμα</b></el> <el>(σάγμα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σάττω'><el>σάττω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>mostly in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>covering: the covering of a shield</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>: <i>a large cloak</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a pack-saddle</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>a pile</i>, <el>ὅπλων</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}